ðŸ¤– elif
#Same as "if else" that uses in C/C++


if "condition1":
  "if condition1 does sth"
elif "condition2":
  "if condition2 does sth"
elif "condition3":
  "if condition3 does sth"
else:
  "if all the conditions are False"
  

- You can use 'elif' whatever you want to declare conditions.

